<p>
<lb n="1"/>ṁ śubhamastu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svasti śrī jayābhyudaya śālivāhana śakavaruṣaṁgaḷu 1479 na(la)
<lb n="2"/>saṁvatsara Āṣāḍha śu 12 lū śrīmatu pratāpa munimaḍagu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/>ju liṁgarasara makkaḷu siṁgapa tirumalaya vīrapa <unclear>svaya</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṁbhudēvarige samarpisida sēve dēvara kāluve gadde be <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/>ḷige saluva hola matu kelau holaṁnu mahi(ja)
<lb n="6" break="no"/>yanikikoṁḍuyiralāgi mahājanaṁgaḷige <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="7"/>keṁdu naṁmataṁde liṁgarasarigeṁ baniviṁma(ṁṇa)
</p>

<p>(Rest is broken and lost).</p>

